[SN]TITLE[SN]
Woman seriously hurt after being hit by Edinburgh bus

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An elderly woman has been taken to hospital with serious injuries after being hit by a bus in Edinburgh.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The woman, who is in her 80s, was struck by the bus in Church Hill Place just after 08:00.
The road was closed but reopened at about 08:45.
